title: en.wikipedia.org_wiki_Template_One_Piece
transformers_text: This template's initial visibility currently defaults to autocollapse meaning that if there is another collapsible item on the page a navbox sidebar or table with the collapsible attribute it is hidden apart from its title bar if not it is fully visible To change this template's initial visibility the state parameter may be used
